  "body": "Is node 19 supported on latest version of hardhat? \r\n\r\nIm getting the following warning when `nom install` into a new hardhat project.\r\n\r\n```\r\nnpm WARN EBADENGINE Unsupported engine {\r\nnpm WARN EBADENGINE   package: 'hardhat@2.12.2',\r\nnpm WARN EBADENGINE   required: { node: '^14.0.0 || ^16.0.0 || ^18.0.0' },\r\nnpm WARN EBADENGINE   current: { node: 'v19.0.1', npm: '8.19.2' }\r\nnpm WARN EBADENGINE }\r\n```\r\n\r\nAlso, when using [slither-actions](https://github.com/marketplace/actions/slither-action) the pipeline fail when installing hardhat 2.12.2 for the same reason\r\n\r\n<img width=\"983\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/14795944/201434092-31de7a2c-7feb-431f-8e74-91ed6bfa4dcf.png\">\r\n",
